Title: Slipknot
Plot: When two high profile murders are linked to each other, Aceveda orders Wyms to get the entire Barn involved before gang and racial violence breaks out.  Mackey uses the case to leverage himself and the Strike Team back into the streets of Farmington.
GuestStars: David Rees Snell, Cathy Cahlin Ryan, Michele Hicks, Noel Gugliemi, Nicki Micheaux, Rashaan Nall, Paul Benjamin, Vincent Angell, Camillia Sanes, Gareth Williams, William Stanford Davis, Dwayne L. Barnes, Andrew B
